            <title>[LU-8809] Print more useful information in LASSERTF() from osp_statfs()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8809</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be better if we had an improved error message for this LASSERT() that printed out the &lt;tt&gt;opd_pre_last_created_fid&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;opd_pre_used_fid&lt;/tt&gt; values, so that we know what kind of values they contain (e.g. something slightly above 40000, or some random value). &lt;/p&gt;</description>
